tion/copy operations to use markup/from/to; added `inheritedReadOnly` to ContextMenuProps.|\n|**Context menu predicates** <br> `packages/app-desktop/gui/NoteEditor/utils/contextMenu.ts`|Simplified `isActive` callbacks for cut/copy to ignore `itemType` (renamed `_itemType`) and rely on presence of `textToCopy`/`htmlToCopy` and read-only state.|\n|**Editor integration (v5/v6)** <br> `packages/app-desktop/gui/NoteEditor/NoteBody/CodeMirror/v5/CodeMirror.tsx`, `.../v6/CodeMirror.tsx`|Propagated `inheritedReadOnly: props.disabled` to useContextMenu and typed `editorRef` as `RefObject<CodeMirrorControl>` in v5; minor type/formatting tweaks in v6.|\n\n## Sequence Diagram(s)\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n  participant Editor\n  participant useContextMenu\n  participant ContextMenu\n  participant getResourceIdFromMarkup\n\n  Editor->>useContextMenu: click at cursorPos (global)\n  useContextMenu->>getResourceIdFromMarkup: getResourceIdFromMarkup(lineContent, cursorPosInLine, lineStartPos)\n  getResourceIdFromMarkup-->>useContextMenu: ResourceMarkupInfo {resourceId,type,markup,from,to}\n  useContextMenu->>ContextMenu: showResourceContextMenu(resourceInfo, markup, from, to, inheritedReadOnly)\n  ContextMenu-->>useContextMenu: user action (copy / open / insert)\n  useContextMenu->>Editor: perform action (copy markup / insert via from-to / open)\n```\n\n## Possibly related PRs\n\n- laurent22/joplin#14402: Modifies the same `getResourceIdFromMarkup` signature and resource-markup/context-menu flow in `useContextMenu.ts`.\n- laurent22/joplin#14209: Earlier changes to CodeMirror context-menu resource extraction and propagation that this PR further extends.\n\n## Suggested labels\n\n`markdown-editor`\n\n</details>\n\n<!-- walkthrough_end -->\n\n\n<!-- pre_merge_checks_walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>🚥 Pre-merge checks | ✅ 2 | ❌ 1</summary>\n\n### ❌ Failed checks (1 warning)\n\n|     Check name     | Status     | Explanation                                               